properties.Name: LineOfCreditStatusType
properties.Description:
The Line Of Credit status of the personal Line Of Credit.

Ex:
CURRENT
Line Of Credit payments are current and paid.

DELINQUENT
Line Of Credit payments are delinquent or unpaid.

IN-DEFAULT
The Line Of Credit is in default due to unpaid payments or failure to comply with the terms and conditions of the Line Of Credit.
